import { Menu, Container, Image, ICon, Icon } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import Link from 'next/link';

function Header() {
  return (
    <Menu fluid id='menu' inverted>
      <Container text>
        <Link href='/'>
          <Menu.Item header>
            <Image
              size='mini'
              src='/static/logo.svg'
              style={{ marginRight: '1em' }}
            />
            ReactReserve
          </Menu.Item>
        </Link>

        <Link href='/cart'>
          <Menu.Item header>
            <Icon size='large' name='cart' />
            Cart
          </Menu.Item>
        </Link>

        <Link href='/account'>
          <Menu.Item header>
            <Icon name='user' size='large' />
            Account
          </Menu.Item>
        </Link>

        <Menu.Item header>
          <Icon name='sign out' size='large' />
          Logout
        </Menu.Item>
      </Container>
    </Menu>
  );
}

export default Header;
